# Full installer image up to kali-linux-large
#
# It should contain everything offered in tasksel
# during initial installation so all kali-linux-* except:
# - kali-linux-everything
#
# ./build.sh --installer --variant large

## Metapackages
# You can customize the set of Kali metapackages (groups of tools)
# available in the installer ISO
# For the complete list see: https://www.kali.org/tools/kali-meta/
kali-linux-core
kali-tools-top10
kali-linux-default
kali-linux-large

